title: #275 Never Stop Improving
itunes:title: #275 Never Stop Improving
description:
Taylor "McGrawless" is in town and hanging with Nikki and Andrew for the pod. They discuss some of 9/11, how seeing the Challenger explode affected Nikki and how EJ set her straight about nuclear war. Andrew cried while watching Top Gun last night and Nikki almost melted when Miles Teller made eye contact with her last month. You Heard It Here First, bad luck on a rollercoaster, an orgasm on a rollercoaster, strange addictions, mind wandering causes depression and Taylor's latest five finger shopping spree. In Nikki's Reddit Dump, they find something out of the Nocte Lupus forum and some stay at home girlfriend ASMR.
